metadata.name: Broken Charlie
metadata.description:
Title: Broken Charlie
Year: 2016
Artist: Chris Kelch
Collection: Quaranta Emozioni
Medium: Photography

Bio:

Chris is a visual effects artist and fine art photographer currently working and living in Austria. He has been creating images for films, commercials and all types of computer graphics for more than 25 years.

He loves colorful pop art and graphic themes, but his work is not limited to any particular style.
